{"tid":1645290,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"我朋友：有人死咗 , 我地全部人都有責任。","createTime":"2019-10-10T23:47:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-11T00:41:20.000Z","uid":34676,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"502fb9ac1ccdf313634ef844105de36c4f041222","tid":1645290,"uid":34676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T23:47:52.000Z","msg":"「每次見到有受害人出嚟哭訴，睇到一單單浮屍嘅新聞，都會提醒自己：係因為我哋未夠努力，係我哋唔願意付出更大嘅成本，先令到佢哋受害。<br />\n<br />\n我哋每一個人都有責任。<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求唔應該等政府回應；五大訴求，應該由香港人推翻呢個政權開始，自己實踐出嚟。」"},{"pid":"f3ab2327cf9551233fe6b4148b2ec2c4f54bb834","tid":1645290,"uid":25108,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T23:48:53.000Z","msg":"要推翻一個政權<br />\n要有外國勢力支援<br />\n加有武器<br />\n香港係兩樣都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71c1e03de139a676938263b9f14d4233ab5b2647","tid":1645290,"uid":319181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T00:41:20.000Z","msg":"唔止謝sir，連er er er sir都&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1644080\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1644080</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}